The '''Great Temple Valley''' was a location on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Barkhesh/Legends|Barkhesh]] which contained a series of ancient temples of an unknown civilization scattered along it. They were similar to the [[Massassi Temple]]s on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]]. This area became the site of a [[Rendezvous on Barkhesh|battle]] between [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] and [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].

